2. **Intuition**: We can use Depth-First Search (DFS) or Breadth-First Search (BFS) to explore each connected island starting from every unvisited land cell. During traversal, we accumulate the values of all cells in the island. After processing the entire island, we check if the accumulated sum is divisible by `k`.

